      public static int mainLoopTerminal​(SimpleGameData game, java.io.BufferedReader entry, boolean end, int choice, int nb_player, int i) throws java.io.IOException
      this function is the main loop of the game when played in terminal mode
      Parameters:
      game - contains the informations of the current game
      entry - allow the player to enter their choice in the terminal
      end - a boolean that become "true" when one of the required conditions are met
      choice - represents the different choices made by the players during the game
      nb_player - the number of player
